        <h2 class="section-title">About Our Expense Tracker</h2>

        <h3>Description</h3>
        <p>Our expense tracker website helps users manage their monthly expenses by tracking expenses, payment methods, and categorizing expenses to provide insights and manage budgets effectively.</p>
        <br></br>
        <h3>Database Structure</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Users</strong>: Manage user details and monthly budgets.</li>
            <li><strong>Transactions</strong>: Record expenses, linking them to categories and payment methods.</li>
            <li><strong>User Transactions</strong>: Pivot table between Users and Transactions where you can see which users are a part of which transactions.</li>
            <li><strong>Expense Categories</strong>: Define categories like rent, groceries, and transportation.</li>
            <li><strong>Payment Methods</strong>: Record payment methods such as credit card, cash, or bank transfer.</li>
        </ul>
